Lemon rice Ingredients:
Sesame oil/ gingelly oil : 2 tablespoons 
Mustard: 1 teaspoon 
Chana dal : 1 tablespoon
Peanut: 2 to 3 tablespoons 
Curry leaves: 1 sprig
Turmeric: 1/2 teaspoon 
Salt : as required 
Asafoetida/ Hing : 1/2 teaspoon 
Lemon juice : 1 whole lemon(big)
Rice : 3 to 4 cups (cooked)
